Commentary Text: Rahul Tewatia to Moeen Ali, out Caught by Riyan Parag!! Huge wicket for RR! Moeen was threatening to really go bonkers but Tewatia nips out the threat. Clever bowling from the leggie, bowls a wider googly and knows that Moeen will target the leg-side boundary with the cross-batted stroke. It's the longer part of the ground though, and the fact that Moeen had to fetch it from a wider line plus the googly meant that he mistimed this a touch. Holes out. Races away past short third man who chases slugglishly and fails to prevent the boundary. What a start for Unadkat and RR!

Commentary Text: Sam Curran to Vohra, out Caught by Jadeja!! This is medicore batting by Vohra. Just before this ball, Jadeja was placed at deep mid-wicket and the opener has played this right into the same fielder's hands. This has been a problem with Vohra this season. He's hitting a couple of impressive shots to start off his innings, but throws his wicket away immediately. Was a short ball by Sam Curran and the right hander pulled it straight to Jadeja who ain't gonna miss out on these easy chances. Vohra c Jadeja b Sam Curran 14(11) [4s-1 6s-1]
